sub_title: CEO | Supervisory Board Member | Advisor | Mentor
summary: Oscar Diele is CEO of Flinders design, online retailer in the Home & Living space. His past experience in C-level roles (CMO & COO) revolve around leading digital transformation programs and setting up and growing e-commerce / marketplace businesses. At companies Wehkamp, eBay, Marktplaats, TomTom and TNT/FedEx, Oscar has made a serious impact by leading and implementing the digital strategy and building & leading teams with an entrepreneurial and scale-up mindset.
